creator: pacamara
descriptionHtml:
Try to manage the messy notifications in your own way.

- View all notifications collection
Don't have to check the notifications in the application.

- View only the notifications that you need
Group various notifications together. You don't have to see all the notifications, do you?

- Hide unnecessary notifications
Hide meaningless notifications in Ali. Hidden notifications won't be visible in the notification drawer!

- Do Not Disturb Mode
Check out the notification drawer! You can easily turn on and off DND mode. Take your own time after work ^^ It's very useful when you're playing games or watching videos ;)

- Notification Level
Set notifications to various levels such as urgent and normal.

- Search
Search all the collected notifications at once.

- Repository
Store notifications in the local database, not external.

- Security
Use pattern lock to prevent someone from peeping at your sensitive notifications.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Release Note v1.1.0 - 2021.04.16
What's new
- Keyworded Group. You can check messages containing some keywords right away.
- Auto Do Not Disturb Mode. Automatically enables DND Mode while using full screen apps(ex. youtube, games, ...)
- Channel now can be assigned to multiple groups
- Improve swipe on New tab cards
Bug fixes
- Not notifying issue of urgent group messages
- Unmatched unread indicator issue
- Fix minor bugs
